# Signature Upload Rules

All signature inputs across the workflow (requester, approver, acknowledge) must follow these unified rules.

## Accepted File Types
- `accept="image/png,image/jpeg,image/jpg"` on every `<input type="file">` for signatures
- JS validation: `['image/png', 'image/jpeg', 'image/jpg'].includes(file.type)`
- Error message: `'Vui lòng chọn file hình ảnh PNG hoặc JPG'`

## Compression (applied before size check)
- Max dimensions: **800 × 400 px** (maintain aspect ratio)
- JPEG quality: **0.7**
- Always fill canvas with **white** before drawing to prevent transparent PNGs turning black when saved as JPEG:

```js
ctx.fillStyle = '#ffffff';
ctx.fillRect(0, 0, width, height);
ctx.drawImage(img, 0, 0, width, height);
const base64 = canvas.toDataURL('image/jpeg', quality);
```

## Max Size After Compression
- **500 KB** (base64 string length)
- Check: `base64Data.length > 500 * 1024`
- Error message: `'Chữ ký vẫn quá lớn sau khi nén (tối đa 500KB). Vui lòng chọn ảnh nhỏ hơn.'`

## Mandatory Scope — Every Submission and Approval

**EVERY submission and EVERY approval action requires a signature upload. No exceptions.**

| Page | Action | Signature required |
|---|---|---|
| `purchase_request.html` | PR submission (requester, Step 3 wizard) | Yes — already implemented |
| `purchase_request.html` | PR approval (approver, drawer) | Yes — approver uploads before clicking Duyệt |
| `voucher.html` | Voucher submission (requester) | Yes — already implemented |
| `voucher.html` | Voucher approval (individual modal) | Yes — already implemented |
| `voucher.html` | Voucher bulk approval | Yes — already implemented |
| `payment_request.html` | Payment request submission | Yes |

### Verification requirement
- Budget / Supplier / Contract approvers: run `compareSignatures` against their registered sample from `Master Company` sheet via `getCompanyApprovers` endpoint. Block if similarity < 75%.
- Purchasing approver (Kế Toán Chi department): no registered sample → upload required but similarity check skipped (same as "no_sample" fallback).
- Requester signatures: no verification against sample needed.

### Sample signature source
- Fetched via `getCompanyApprovers` action → `TLCG_CASH_BACKEND.gs` → Master Company sheet columns F (legalRep), J (accountant), N (treasurer)
- Approver email matched against `legalRep.email`, `accountant.email`, `treasurer.email` to find the correct sample URL.

## Files Affected
- `voucher.html` — requester signature, approver modal signature, bulk approver signature, acknowledge signature
- `purchase_request.html` — requester signature (Step 3), approver signature (drawer)
- `payment_request.html` — any signature inputs
- `approve_voucher.html`, `reject_voucher.html`, `approve_payment_request.html`, `reject_payment_request.html`
